{
  "stem": "20848.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "My mother was searched in the most unbelievable places.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I don't know what they were searching for.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And there were very, very-- the Germans.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "They were Germans-- and they were women.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "They were very rough and tough, and they were screaming and yelling.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And I was absolutely petrified.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I beg pardon?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, I think so.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes, we must have been all Jewish, yes.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that was the very first time, I think, I came across such a brutality, you know, that actually-- and nevertheless, we got-- it was very cold already.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was a very cold winter that year.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we went to Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And my father was-- had already a little flat for us prepared.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We didn't take very much with us to Warsaw at all.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I think we left everything behind.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We had a terrible lot of materials, you know?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We had whole [? shelves ?] of materials, because when customers used to come, they used to, you know, choose what material they want to have their garments made of.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We had a lot of beautiful English materials, which the Germans took.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I think we left everything.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We had a very nice apartment.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But they used to come every so often to his apartment, the Germans, while we were still there.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they wanted to take furniture out.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "You see, they were taking furniture out from our house where we're leaving.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And this house was a huge, huge house with a courtyard.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I don't know how many tenants were there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But there was these lorries there day and night loading things, robbing things, you know, from the people-- furniture and Persian carpets.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And whatever, you know, properties the people had, the Germans were taking.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
